casebody.data:
Schlesinger et al., Respondents, v. Christian et al., Appellants. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. March 31, 1892.) Action by Charles Schlesinger and others against William A. Christian and others.

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and O’Brien and Ingraham, JJ.

No opinion. • Motion to dismiss appeal granted, with $10 costs.
